channel.title: Cant connect to my server?
channel.description:
Hi guys, well basically i made a server (317 old school) , port forwarded, did everything right... i tested on status checker and it sayd online! but one prob im having is when i try to connect to my server via a ip changer client, it dosent work. iv tried every possible method , i tried changing all ip's in the source to the no-ip the 0.0.0.0 the 127.0.0.1 and still DOSENT WORK! if anyone has teamveiwer here to help me with it, i will love them forever!
thanks..

item.title: Cant connect to my server?
item.dc:creator: @The_Web_Guy The Web Guy
item.description:
@The_Web_Guy wrote:

Make sure client is connecting to the same port the server is listening on. By default it’s 43594, however, some 317s use 5555.
